string.text:
%c[0,153,255,255]The control settings%c[0,140,140,140] now include the following %c[0,0,255,30]new features:\n%c[0,140,140,140]
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]quick knife strike;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]quick grenade throw;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]quick bolt throw;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]alternative aiming (if an optical sight is installed);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]wiping the helmet mask (gas mask);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]unloading all weapons in the inventory (weapons in slots are excluded);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]radial menu for selecting hand grenades;			
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]companion menu (for quickly issuing commands);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]campfire cooking menu;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]enable/disable the minimap and interface;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]enable/disable the compass (appears when the compass add-on is enabled);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]enable/disable the helmet visor;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]temporary display of the interface;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]holding breath while aiming;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]ability to drop the backpack (RBS);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]ability to change the minimap zoom level;
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]ability to clear a specific key binding in the control options (hover over the desired key and press RMB);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]ability to change how the sprint key works (like in the original—press once—or like in modern games—hold);
\n%c[0,200,0,255]• %c[0,140,140,140]ability to transfer multiple items at once (hold Left CTRL or Left ALT or Left SHIFT + double-click LMB on the desired item).
